reviewText: I thought my 2 year old son would love it, but he watched it only twice and put it back on the shelf. Not sure what the problem was. I must not have been captivated by it either, since I cannot recall what it was about, while other Sesame Street DVD's I remember by heart!
I sent this DVD (along with 6 other "Big Bird" DVDs) to a child who has never experienced Big Bird.  She'll open them all up on Christmas Day - and I'm certain she won't be disappointed.
